Description: X.Org X server -- nested display driver
 This package provides a nested display driver, which allows Xorg
 to run on top of another X server, just like Xephyr.
 .
 More information about X.Org can be found at:
 <URL:http://www.X.org>
 .
 This package is based on xserver-xorg-video-dummy.
